[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    161[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    162[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Severity:** NOTE
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    163[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **File:** `chapter12.09-python-example.md`, `SEIRCompartmentalModel.forecast` and `StatisticalARIMABaseline.forecast`
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    164[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
